metadata.name: Shortcut #43
metadata.description:
Shortcuts are an invitation to embrace the uncharted, to question established norms, and to embark on a voyage of discovery. They remind us that the journey itself holds immeasurable value, challenging us to reconsider possibilities and find our true selves along the way.

Press 's' to save high resolution png

Created using p5js.

@bubicart, May, 2023

metadata.name: Earth Bitmaps #4
metadata.description:
Earth Bitmaps - Pixelated Earth; Imagination Art Animation 

Earth Bitmaps presents a collection that explores the intricate pixelated patterns and textures found in the natural world. From the mesmerizing ripples on a sandy beach to the vibrant veins of a leaf, this collection celebrates the artistry inherent in Earth's landscapes.

Token management in live mode:

Click "s" to save PNG image (3240x3240px PNG)

Click "g" to render GIF animation (240 frames 20 sec. 1080x1080px animation)

Earth Bitmaps by Casia 2023

metadata.name: SILENCE! #421
metadata.description:
Shut up and look at art.

Have you ever noticed that to have silence you need noise?

This project wants to let you think about this dichotomy!

There can't be silence without noise, but the noisiest art can be completely silent.

---

This project is completely realized procedurally/generatively with vanilla JS (canvas)

You can save/open a 4096px² render of the artwork by right-clicking on it

easter-egg: If you type the name of the project inside it an art critic and aesthete will appear!
